      "content": "## Test Results\n\n- **zx Globals Test**: {{zxGlobalsTest}}\n- **Shell Commands Test**: {{shellCommandsTest}}\n- **Working Directory Test**: {{workingDirTest}}\n- **FS Operations Test**: {{fsOperationsTest}}\n- **Stdout Capture Test**: {{stdoutCaptureTest}}\n- **Console Log Test**: {{consoleLogTest}}\n\n## Usage Instructions\n\n1. **Shell Integration**: All zx globals available (`$`, `cd`, `echo`, `chalk`, etc.)\n2. **Working Directory**: Shell commands executed in notebook directory\n3. **Global Output**: **View → Toggle Output Panel** or **Ctrl+Shift+`** to toggle the global output panel that captures all stdout/stderr\n4. **Console Viewer**: **View → Toggle Console Viewer** or **Ctrl+`** to toggle the console viewer that captures all console.log output\n5. **File Operations**: All operations scoped to notebook directory\n\n## Key Differences\n\n- **Output Panel** (**Ctrl+Shift+`**): Captures raw stdout/stderr from shell commands and direct process writes\n- **Console Viewer** (**Ctrl+`**): Captures console.log/warn/error/info/debug with rich object display\n- Console logs persist across cell re-executions and show execution order\n- Both panels support auto-scroll and manual clearing\n- Panels accessible via **View menu** (toolbar buttons removed)"
